This paper is about improving the efficiency and effectiveness of Batch Normalization (BN) and Decorrelated Batch Normalization (DBN) in neural network training. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computer Science related to machine learning and deep learning, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Among these sub-categories, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely ones, as they are directly related to the topic of the paper. The other sub-categories are also relevant, as they involve techniques and applications of machine learning and deep learning.
